  m_text: "\u2022 Be aware that attackers use various social engineering tactics
    like phishing, brute force, dictionary attacks, credential stuffing, and pretexting.
    \r\n\r\n\u2022 Criminals often try to trick you into revealing your password,
    as it's often easier to exploit human nature.  \r\n\r\n\u2022 Always be suspicious
    of unexpected requests for sensitive information, even if they seem to come from
    someone you know or a trusted company.  \r\n\r\n\u2022 Never share your password
    in response to an email or phone call, even if it seems legitimate. \r\n\r\n\u2022
    To access important services like banking, always go directly to their official
    website using your own saved bookmark or by typing the correct web address yourself. "
